snippet.title: Pikmin 3 Wii U Hack: Extra Side of Stories OFFICIAL TRAILER - [Demo Available]
snippet.description:
Download: https://drive.google.com/file/d/1eUunVT_pxnn041eWyF3U7ekF-SX8oWCy/view?usp=sharing
Welcome to the Demo of Extra Side of Stories. A Pikmin 3 Mission Mode hack, that aims to replace all 15 collect treasure with new remixed stages in this story called: Olimar's Mission, where Olimar wants to collect enough money to buy back his beloved S.S. Dolphin. 
This Demo only features 3 playable levels now.
#Pikmin3Hack #SideStories
